[
    {
        "text": "So a few years ago, my eyes were opened to the dark side of the construction industry.",
        "startTime": 5713,
        "endTime": 9674,
        "slowStartTime": 8719,
        "slowEndTime": 14736
    },
    {
        "text": "In 2006, young Qatari students took me to go and see the migrant worker camps.",
        "startTime": 10560,
        "endTime": 15817,
        "slowStartTime": 15990,
        "slowEndTime": 23951
    },
    {
        "text": "And since then I've followed the unfolding issue of worker rights.",
        "startTime": 16266,
        "endTime": 20148,
        "slowStartTime": 24549,
        "slowEndTime": 30447
    },
    {
        "text": "In the last six months, more than 300 skyscrapers in the UAE have been put on hold or canceled.",
        "startTime": 20485,
        "endTime": 25321,
        "slowStartTime": 30878,
        "slowEndTime": 38207
    },
    {
        "text": "Behind the headlines that lay behind these buildings...",
        "startTime": 26172,
        "endTime": 28921,
        "slowStartTime": 39408,
        "slowEndTime": 43607
    },
    {
        "text": "...is the fate of the often-indentured construction worker,...",
        "startTime": 29017,
        "endTime": 31572,
        "slowStartTime": 43675,
        "slowEndTime": 47583
    },
    {
        "text": "...1.1 million of them.",
        "startTime": 32524,
        "endTime": 33849,
        "slowStartTime": 48936,
        "slowEndTime": 50998
    },
    {
        "text": "Mainly Indian, Pakistani, Sri Lankan, and Nepalese, these laborers risk everything...",
        "startTime": 34913,
        "endTime": 39546,
        "slowStartTime": 52520,
        "slowEndTime": 59544
    },
    {
        "text": "...to make money for their families back home.",
        "startTime": 39956,
        "endTime": 41841,
        "slowStartTime": 60084,
        "slowEndTime": 62987
    },
    {
        "text": "They pay a middleman thousands of dollars to be there.",
        "startTime": 42459,
        "endTime": 44706,
        "slowStartTime": 63838,
        "slowEndTime": 67284
    },
    {
        "text": "And when they arrive, they find themselves in labor camps with no water,...",
        "startTime": 45297,
        "endTime": 48077,
        "slowStartTime": 68096,
        "slowEndTime": 72340
    },
    {
        "text": "...no air conditioning and their passports taken away.",
        "startTime": 48742,
        "endTime": 51564,
        "slowStartTime": 73263,
        "slowEndTime": 77571
    },
    {
        "text": "While it's easy to point the finger at local officials and higher authorities,...",
        "startTime": 52991,
        "endTime": 56681,
        "slowStartTime": 79636,
        "slowEndTime": 85246
    },
    {
        "text": "...99 percent of these people are hired by the private sector.",
        "startTime": 56953,
        "endTime": 59587,
        "slowStartTime": 85579,
        "slowEndTime": 89605
    },
    {
        "text": "And then the financial collapse happened.",
        "startTime": 60289,
        "endTime": 62036,
        "slowStartTime": 90583,
        "slowEndTime": 93279
    },
    {
        "text": "When the contractors had gone bust,...",
        "startTime": 63003,
        "endTime": 64666,
        "slowStartTime": 94654,
        "slowEndTime": 97224
    },
    {
        "text": "...as they'd been overleveraged like everyone else,...",
        "startTime": 64821,
        "endTime": 66728,
        "slowStartTime": 97381,
        "slowEndTime": 100317
    },
    {
        "text": "...the difference is everything goes missing,...",
        "startTime": 67355,
        "endTime": 68969,
        "slowStartTime": 101183,
        "slowEndTime": 103678
    },
    {
        "text": "...documentation, passports, and tickets home for these workers.",
        "startTime": 69759,
        "endTime": 73754,
        "slowStartTime": 104788,
        "slowEndTime": 110856
    },
    {
        "text": "Currently right now, thousands of workers are abandoned.",
        "startTime": 74279,
        "endTime": 77639,
        "slowStartTime": 111569,
        "slowEndTime": 116684
    },
    {
        "text": "There's no way back home.",
        "startTime": 78008,
        "endTime": 79217,
        "slowStartTime": 117162,
        "slowEndTime": 119051
    },
    {
        "text": "And there is no way and no proof of arrival.",
        "startTime": 79765,
        "endTime": 82140,
        "slowStartTime": 119797,
        "slowEndTime": 123435
    },
    {
        "text": "These are the boom and bust refugees.",
        "startTime": 82957,
        "endTime": 85218,
        "slowStartTime": 124585,
        "slowEndTime": 128052
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's not forget who's really paying the price of this financial collapse.",
        "startTime": 86187,
        "endTime": 89279,
        "slowStartTime": 129431,
        "slowEndTime": 134143
    },
    {
        "text": "And that as we worry about our next job in the office,...",
        "startTime": 90120,
        "endTime": 92499,
        "slowStartTime": 135330,
        "slowEndTime": 138973
    },
    {
        "text": "...the next design that we can get to keep our workers,...",
        "startTime": 92773,
        "endTime": 95043,
        "slowStartTime": 139309,
        "slowEndTime": 142790
    },
    {
        "text": "...let's not forget these men who are truly dying to work.",
        "startTime": 95777,
        "endTime": 98790,
        "slowStartTime": 143816,
        "slowEndTime": 148410
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you.",
        "startTime": 99318,
        "endTime": 99656,
        "slowStartTime": 149127,
        "slowEndTime": 149709
    }
]